  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"/assets/library/olmo-3.1/8d27e58b-a05f-4ffd-94d2-cd61a48e7303\" alt=\"Olmo3.png\"/></p>\n\n<p>Olmo 3.1 models are available either as a 32B parameter thinking or instruct model. It has long chain-of-thought thinking to improve reasoning tasks like math and coding.</p>\n\n<p>Olmo is a series of Open language models designed to enable the science of language models.\nThese models are pre-trained on the Dolma 3 dataset and post-trained on the Dolci datasets. Allen AI team is releasing all code, checkpoints, logs, and associated training details.</p>\n\n<h3>Models</h3>\n\n<p><strong>Olmo 3.1 Instruct 32B</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>ollama run olmo-3.1:32b-instruct\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Olmo 3.1 Think 32B</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>ollama run olmo-3.1:32b-think\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>Benchmark</h3>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Benchmark</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Olmo 3.1 32B Think</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Olmo 3 Think 32B</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Qwen 3 32B</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Qwen 3 VL 32B Thinking</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Qwen 2.5 32B</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Gemma 3 27B Instruct</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Gemma 2 27B Instruct</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Olmo 2 32B Instruct</th>\n<th align=\"right\">DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-32B</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Math</strong></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td>MATH</td>\n<td align=\"right\">96.2</td>\n<td align=\"right\">96.1</td>\n<td align=\"right\">95.4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">96.7</td>\n<td align=\"right\">80.2</td>\n<td align=\"right\">87.4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">51.5</td>\n<td align=\"right\">49.2</td>\n<td align=\"right\">92.6</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td>AIME 2024</td>\n<td align=\"right\">80.6</td